data.description: Location, location, location! Shorten your commute - within 10 minutes to Downtown/Midtown/Univ of Houston, Minute Maid Park and BBVA Compass Stadium. This immaculate townhome in small gated complex in established neighborhood and thriving area is well-packaged with a bedroom and bathroom on each floor, stunning 10 ceilings, gorgeous hardwood floors throughout, no carpet, granite countertops in kitchen and all bathrooms. Kitchen well-packaged with island, breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances. Radiant attic barrier, tankless water and 16 seer HVAC. Smart floorplan, perfect for . Move in ready with washer, dryer and fridge. Schedule your appointment today! NO HOA - high investment and AirBNB potential!
